1- Create a key pair:
On the search navigator search for EC2.
click on Key Pairs.
then click on Create key pair.
name your key.
pem is the file format.
then click on Create key pair, a file will be downloaded. Keep that file on a safe place you will use it to connect to the instance.

2-	Manage subscription:
On the search navigator search marketplace
Click on Discover products
On the search bar search Debian 9
Click on Debian GNU/Linux 9 (Stretch)
Then click on Continue to Subscribe.

